      "content": "wait r u sure?? it doesn't even feel that bad, just a bit uncomfortable. i've had bad cramps before and they felt pretty similar. the er is so expensive and i'm literally right in the middle of a long shift at work. can i just take a double dose of ibuprofen to see if it goes away in an hour? i'd rather just deal with it here than drive all the way to the hospital for nothing.",
