      "content": "look i hear you but i really can't afford to leave work right now. if i just take a really strong painkiller like the codeine i have at home, won't that just help me get through the shift? if the pain stops i'll know it was just gas and i'll be fine by tomorrow morning. surely a little bit of medicine won't hurt if it just helps me manage the discomfort for a few hours?",
